{"id":246560,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":10,"day":26}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"128","ytitle":"","mtitle":"美满婚姻","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>丁深</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1951\\10\\51aq070601.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>丁深　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(四)成亲后，押弟子心里尽管不称心，但还得像牛一样替家里干活，并且不断受婆婆的打骂。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1951\\10\\51aq070602.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(五)直到今年，押弟子在土地改革以后分了一亩五分田，并遵照婚姻法，才和芮家的小丈夫离婚。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1951\\10\\51aq070603.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(六)不久，押弟子就和原先和她感情很好的本村农民于道毛结了婚。</FONT>"}]}